     3	//
     4	// Operators and agents asking "is the worker still working beads?" must be
     5	// able to answer the question for one project at a time. A global process
     6	// scan ("ps aux | grep ddx work") returns workers from every checkout on the
     7	// machine and produces a misleading "yes, working" signal when the worker
     8	// belongs to a different repository. This package filters live workers by
